ght
hspace=3D12 v:shapes=3D"Picture_x0020_1"><![endif]><span lang=3DEN-GB
style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-no-proof:yes'>Population Policies prov=
ide
control over which alien races you allow at your colonies.<o:p></o:p></span=
></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;ms=
o-no-proof:
yes'>Population policies can be set in the Colonies screen (F2), in the
Population tab.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;ms=
o-no-proof:
yes'>There are two policy settings per colony:<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoListParagraphCxSpFirst style=3D'text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l=
0 level1 lfo2'><![if !supportLists]><span
lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-fareast-font-family:Verdana;mso-bidi-font-family:=
Verdana;
mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-no-proof:yes'><span style=3D'mso-list:Ignore'>1=
.<span
style=3D'font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></s=
pan><![endif]><span
lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-no-proof:yes'>Global sett=
ing that
applies to all other races (except your race)<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoListParagraphCxSpLast style=3D'text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0=
 level1 lfo2'><![if !supportLists]><span
lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-fareast-font-family:Verdana;mso-bidi-font-family:=
Verdana;
mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-no-proof:yes'><span style=3D'mso-list:Ignore'>2=
.<span
style=3D'font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></s=
pan><![endif]><span
lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-no-proof:yes'>Same race f=
amily as
your own. This allows you to have harsh settings for races not in your race
family, but kinder policies for races of your race family<o:p></o:p></span>=
</p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;ms=
o-no-proof:
yes'>The five different population policy settings are described below.<o:p=
></o:p></span></p>

<h3><span lang=3DEN-GB>Assimilate</span></h3>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;ms=
o-no-proof:
yes'>Assimilate means to accept these races into your empire. This is the
default setting.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<h3><span lang=3DEN-GB>Do Not Accept</span></h3>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;ms=
o-no-proof:
yes'>Do not allow migration of these races to the colony. This will prevent
passenger ships from dropping off migrants from these races at the colony.<=
o:p></o:p></span></p>

<h3><span lang=3DEN-GB>Resettle</span></h3>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;ms=
o-no-proof:
yes'>Actively migrate these races away from the colony to other colonies th=
at
will accept them. Passenger ships will pick up these races from the colony.=
<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape id=3D"Picture_x0020_0" o:s=
pid=3D"_x0000_s1026"
 type=3D"#_x0000_t75" style=3D'position:absolute;margin-left:254.6pt;margin=
-top:0;
 width:305.8pt;height:46.75pt;z-index:251658240;visibility:visible;
 mso-wrap-style:square;mso-width-percent:0;mso-height-percent:0;
 mso-wrap-distance-left:9pt;mso-wrap-distance-top:0;mso-wrap-distance-right=
:9pt;
 mso-wrap-distance-bottom:0;mso-position-horizontal:right;
 mso-position-horizontal-relative:text;mso-position-vertical:absolute;
 mso-position-vertical-relative:text;mso-width-percent:0;mso-height-percent=
:0;
 mso-width-relative:page;mso-height-relative:page'>
 <v:imagedata src=3D"GameConcepts_ColonyPopulationPolicies_files/image003.p=
ng"
  o:title=3D""/>
 <w:wrap type=3D"square"/>
</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=3D408 height=3D62
src=3D"GameConcepts_ColonyPopulationPolicies_files/image004.png" align=3Dri=
ght
hspace=3D12 v:shapes=3D"Picture_x0020_0"><![endif]><span lang=3DEN-GB
style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;mso-no-proof:yes'>If you have enabled the =
empire
policy setting &quot;Use Penal Colonies to implement Enslave policy&quot; t=
hen
these unwanted races will be migrated to Penal colonies for enslavement the=
re.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<h3><span lang=3DEN-GB>Enslave</span></h3>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;ms=
o-no-proof:
yes'>Enslaves these races, forcing them into hard labor. When a race is
enslaved at a colony it&#8217;s growth rate will be zero.<o:p></o:p></span>=
</p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;ms=
o-no-proof:
yes'>For each race that you enslave, the corresponding empires of those rac=
es
will take offense at your actions. The amount of offense is directly relate=
d to
the population amount that you enslave.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;ms=
o-no-proof:
yes'>Enslavement also provides a bonus to the colony's economy. The amount =
of
the bonus depends on the proportion of the total population that is enslave=
d,
up to a maximum of 50% if all of the population is enslaved.<o:p></o:p></sp=
an></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;ms=
o-no-proof:
yes'>If you have enabled the empire policy setting &quot;Use Penal Colonies=
 to
implement Enslave policy&quot; then some of your colonies will automaticall=
y be
set as Penal Colonies (policy set to Enslave). Your other colonies with pol=
icy
set to Resettle will migrate their unwanted races to the Penal colonies for
enslavement.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<h3><span lang=3DEN-GB>Exterminate</span></h3>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;ms=
o-no-proof:
yes'>Steadily eliminates these races at the colony, reducing their populati=
on
until it reaches zero. When a race is being exterminated at a colony it&#82=
17;s
growth rate will be zero.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;ms=
o-no-proof:
yes'>For each race that you are exterminating, the corresponding empires of
those races will take deep offense at your actions. The amount of offense is
directly related to the population amount that you exterminate.<o:p></o:p><=
/span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;ms=
o-no-proof:
yes'>Exterminating races will also negatively impact your empire's reputati=
on
&#8211; all other empire&#8217;s will be offended by your harsh actions.<o:=
p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>

